title: Muriel 3.0
text:
Lose [click], [click], [click]: Break up to 3 subroutines on this ice. Only the Runner can use this ability.
[subroutine] The Corp gets +1 allotted [click] for their next turn.
[subroutine] Gain 1[credit].
[subroutine] You may draw one card, and/or shuffle one card from Archives or HQ into R&D.
[subroutine] End the run.
